<!------------------------------------------------
Concept Behind designing this pattern:
1.	Created a table with heading, 
2.	For inner row i take a list inside another cell
and nested a table inside it
3. For 1st column with managers with there team members, i created a list name and member inside it, which will toggle when clicked on manager name.
4. for permission i.e selectbox, i created TD cell in front of the name to match the allignments.
5. Repeated Same for next managers.
------------------------------------------------->

<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $(document).on('keypress', '#mainForm input', function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode == $.ui.keyCode.ENTER) {
                   $('#save-bill-info').trigger('click');
            }
        });
        $(document).on('keypress', '#mainFormProject input', function(e) {
            if (e.keyCode == $.ui.keyCode.ENTER) {
                   $('#save-bill-project').trigger('click');
            }
        });
    });
</script>

function autoDailyEmpShowData(showFlag) {
    var dtText = $("#daterangepicker_start").val();
    var url = '/poc/fetchAllEmpName';
    var idSearch = jQuery("#txtName");
    if (showFlag == 1) { // When engineer time sheet search proceed
        idSearch = jQuery("#engTimeSearch");
    } else if (showFlag == 3) {// Hierarchy 
        idSearch = $("#empNameSearchEmp");
    }
    idSearch.autocomplete({
        source: url+'?startDt='+dtText,
        minLength: 0,
        dataType: "json",
        focus: function (event, ui) {
            //htmlDecodeDataLabelSetting(ui.item.label);
            return false;
        },
        select: function (event, ui) {
            if (showFlag != 3) {
                jQuery("#searchEmpId").val(ui.item.empNum);
                var empId = $("#searchEmpId").val();
                htmlDecodeDataLabelSetting(ui.item.label, showFlag);
                if (showFlag == 2) {
                    $("#search-form").submit();
                    event.preventDefault();
                } else {
                    loadCalendar();
                }
            } else {
                jQuery("#engineerNameSearchEmpIdEmp").val(ui.item.empNum);
                htmlDecodeDataLabelSetting(ui.item.label, showFlag);
            }
            return false;
        }
    });
}
function htmlDecodeDataLabelSetting(label, showFlag) {
    var regExp = /\(([^)]+)\)/;
    var matches = regExp.exec(label);
    var lblSplit = label.split(matches[0]);
    var actualLabel = label;
    label = lblSplit[0];
    var idSearch = jQuery("#txtName");
    if (showFlag == 1) { // When engineer time sheet search proceed
        idSearch = jQuery("#engTimeSearch");
        $("#searchContainerTxt").html(actualLabel);
    } else if (showFlag == 3) {
        idSearch = jQuery("#empNameSearchEmp");
    }
    idSearch.val(label);
}

    function search()
    {
        var searchText = $(".search-uni").val();
        searchText = $.trim(searchText);
        if (searchText.length &gt;= 1) {
            $(".search-reset").show();
            if ($(".search-result-uni").is(":hidden")) {

                $('.search-result-uni').show(100);
            }
        } else {
            $(".search-result-uni").hide(100);
            $(".search-reset").hide();
        }
    }
    function reset_search()
    {
        $(".search-uni").val('');
        $(".search-uni").keyup();
        $(".search-reset").hide();
    }
    function rrrrsize() {
        var menuHeight = $(".menu-wrapper ul.sidebar-menu").height();
        console.log(menuHeight + 'px');
        $(".body-wrapper").css("min-height", menuHeight + 'px');
    }
